Thank you for sharing this but could you seed this a bit longer so I can help you with the sharing?

Thanks a lot!

Mexri tora edosa pano apo 100GB apo grigori grammi. Apo adsl pou dokimasa na to katevaso, xekinaei arga me 100 KB/s alla tora pou eimai sto 40% paei arketa kala me 500+ KB/s Tin allo fora tha valo kai gigabit grammi na min exete parapono ;p
Ευχαριστώ πάρα πολύ. Συνεχίστε την καλή δουλειά.
mia erwtisi..tha mporouses na anevaseis k alla epeisodia? i eisai anagkasmenos na ta vazeis 1 fora tin evdomada?
Kathe vdomada kikloforei kai ena epeisodio apo gnosto periodiko.
